Package org.variantsync.diffdetective.preliminary.evaluation

Class GDEvaluator

java.lang.Object
org.variantsync.diffdetective.preliminary.evaluation.GDEvaluator
@Deprecated public class GDEvaluator extends Object
Deprecated.
Class for evaluating GDAnalysisResults.

This class offers methods for calculating metrics from an analysis result, exporting data, and printing the evaluation.
